2022 felt like a bounce back year for me. I got to tour a bit which brought back some familiar feels, and I also was busy with @stephenbradleyphoto, which is something that has given me great pride. A shoutout to all the wonderful, interesting, loving, and caring people in my life. Hopefully, I get to see more of you all in 2023.
And finally, @kristin.lee.bradley ,I love you to bits angel! Thank you for being my best friend, and supporter:))

It's finally here y'all!!! I co-wrote and produced this song with long time friend and fellow musician @about_face_music. Back In Budapest, is a song starting with an idea he had, inspired by a relocation to the city of Budapest. Most of this was done at the tail end of the lockdown, and it was therapidic to be able to create this remotely. Shoutouts to @derekfrankbass , @jay_diggzz , @jacksonallenguitar @scorpionomari @vogaviki @anneliphoto , @9_dragonsstudios, for your talent, time, and energy you put into making this song speak! #stephenbradleymusic #aboutface #budapest #travelbudapest #backinbudapest #funmusic #anthem #budapestmusic #travelmusic #adventuremusic #trendingmusic #trendingmusic #wanderlust #expatmusic #expatlifestyle #budapesttourism #budapesttravel #damestravel

In case you missed it, here is a short clip of the new song 'Back in Budapest' that I produced and co-wrote with long-time friend and collaborator @about_face_music.Inspired by his relocation to the beautiful city of #budapest, its a love letter to an eastern european jewel. Next time you are there, make sure to crank this up on the airpods or 🔊 speakers!! #budapest #budapesthungary #travelbudapest #travelmusic #wanderlustbudapest #stephenbradleymusic #stephenbradleymedia #backinbudapest #budapestmusic #hungary🇭🇺
